265
00:16:03,629 --> 00:16:06,229
Well, who do you think we are?

266
00:16:06,700 --> 00:16:07,930
Why don't you make a guess?

267
00:16:08,900 --> 00:16:10,300
Is this because of money?

268
00:16:10,599 --> 00:16:12,439
If it is,
I'll give you everything I have.

269
00:16:12,440 --> 00:16:15,570
Man, are you treating us
like some petty thieves?

270
00:16:15,869 --> 00:16:18,540
We don't need your money.
Your body will do fine.

271
00:16:19,749 --> 00:16:21,780
I wonder how much we'll get for you.

272
00:16:21,849 --> 00:16:23,378
It's a waste to sell you off
to an island.

273
00:16:23,379 --> 00:16:25,420
Hey. Who would buy her?

274
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:38,700
I did nothing wrong.

275
00:16:39,570 --> 00:16:41,800
Gosh, what a surprise.

276
00:16:42,300 --> 00:16:44,200
You caught on faster than I thought.

277
00:16:44,469 --> 00:16:45,599
Let me go.

278
00:16:46,540 --> 00:16:49,608
I did nothing wrong
to be dragged here like this.

279
00:16:49,609 --> 00:16:51,640
Hey, you brat. Hey.

280
00:16:51,839 --> 00:16:54,179
That's for us to decide.

281
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:56,978
How can a government organization
abduct a civilian like this...

282
00:16:56,979 --> 00:16:59,749
without even telling me
what I did wrong?

283
00:17:02,790 --> 00:17:06,119
Why do all of you
blabber on so annoyingly?

284
00:17:07,430 --> 00:17:10,330
Shall I make you shut your mouth?

285
00:17:11,930 --> 00:17:13,430
Go on and try it.

286
00:17:14,269 --> 00:17:15,728
I'll tell the press...

287
00:17:15,729 --> 00:17:18,170
