294
00:18:38,519 --> 00:18:41,519
You see,
compared to other countries,

295
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:43,620
Germany's visa screening process is
a lot stricter.

296
00:18:44,360 --> 00:18:46,589
There are communists
who try to defect to North Korea...

297
00:18:46,590 --> 00:18:48,660
through East Germany.

298
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:53,529
That's why...

299
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:56,940
we must look closely into...

300
00:18:57,539 --> 00:18:59,859
