have participated in any protests...

301
00:19:02,009 --> 00:19:03,979
and what kind of ideology
they believe in.

302
00:19:06,479 --> 00:19:08,009
Are you doing this...

303
00:19:09,650 --> 00:19:11,880
because of Hee Tae?

304
00:19:18,819 --> 00:19:20,689
Defeat the Yushin remnants!

305
00:19:20,690 --> 00:19:22,329
- Defeat the Yushin remnants!
- Defeat the Yushin remnants!

306
00:19:22,330 --> 00:19:24,058
