307
00:19:24,059 --> 00:19:25,998
- End the martial law!
- End the martial law!

308
00:19:25,999 --> 00:19:28,099
- We say no...
- We say no...

309
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:30,340
- to martial law!
- To martial law!

310
00:19:30,499 --> 00:19:32,238
End the martial law!

311
00:19:32,239 --> 00:19:34,268
- End the martial law!
- End the martial law!

312
00:19:34,269 --> 00:19:35,370
Defeat...

313
00:19:35,940 --> 00:19:37,640
Step down!

314
00:19:37,940 --> 00:19:40,748
Why are they protesting
in broad daylight?

315
00:19:40,749 --> 00:19:44,049
- We say no to martial law!
- We say no to martial law!

316
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:46,349
End the martial law!

317
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:48,488
- End the martial law!
- End the martial law!

318
00:19:48,489 --> 00:19:50,419
