319
00:19:50,420 --> 00:19:52,089
- Defeat the Yushin remnants!
- Defeat the Yushin remnants!

320
00:19:52,090 --> 00:19:54,329
- Myeong Hee.
- End the martial law!

321
00:19:54,330 --> 00:19:56,429
- End the martial law!
- End the martial law!

322
00:19:56,430 --> 00:19:58,599
- We say no...
- We say no...

323
00:19:58,600 --> 00:20:00,830
- to martial law!
- To martial law!

324
00:20:03,029 --> 00:20:07,039
Soo Chan. I don't mean to be rude,

