338
00:21:15,370 --> 00:21:18,509
It's not like you violated
the National Security Act.

339
00:21:19,140 --> 00:21:22,009
Myeong Hee,
don't worry and just wait.

340
00:21:22,950 --> 00:21:25,249
I'll find a way somehow.

341
