00:23:05,819 --> 00:23:08,390
- You're getting ahead of yourself.
- Goodness.

358
00:23:08,519 --> 00:23:11,660
Gosh. You're one to talk.

359
00:23:12,690 --> 00:23:15,959
Weren't you asking about his parents
when we just met him?

360
00:23:16,289 --> 00:23:18,630
I wasn't getting ahead of myself.
I just...

361
00:23:19,860 --> 00:23:21,170
Whatever.

362
00:23:25,370 --> 00:23:26,769
Goodness, Myeong Hee!

363
00:23:27,309 --> 00:23:31,080
Welcome home, sweetie.
It's been so long.

364
00:23:32,979 --> 00:23:36,208
