until a moment ago.

366
00:23:40,049 --> 00:23:42,090
Oh, dear.
They must've missed each other.

367
00:23:42,890 --> 00:23:44,819
Anyway, have you eaten?

368
00:23:52,400 --> 00:23:55,700
Why are you so out of it?
You look like you've seen a ghost.

369
00:23:56,529 --> 00:23:58,100
Myeong Hee, is everything okay?

370
00:24:00,309 --> 00:24:01,340
What happened?

371
00:24:03,170 --> 00:24:06,880
It doesn't matter why.
You can't leave the country anyway.

372
00:24:10,880 --> 00:24:12,749
(Kim Hyun Chul)

373
00:24:13,749 --> 00:24:15,690
(Daughter, Kim Myeong Hee)

374
00:24:15,920 --> 00:24:18,789
(Convicted of violating
the National Security Act in 1954)

375
00:24:33,100 --> 00:24:34,840
There's no way...

376
00:24:35,140 --> 00:24:37,610
a commie's daughter will be allowed
to go to Germany.

377
00:24:38,610 --> 00:24:39,979
No way.

378
00:24:40,509 --> 00:24:41,748
My father can't...

379
00:24:41,749 --> 00:24:43,680
Have you ever wondered...

