391
00:25:29,160 --> 00:25:30,459
I'm not sure...

392
00:25:32,529 --> 00:25:34,568
what you've heard and from whom...

393
00:25:34,569 --> 00:25:36,200
Father, you tell me.

394
00:25:37,799 --> 00:25:39,539
Is that true or not?

395
00:25:50,180 --> 00:25:51,850
Why did you never tell me?

396
00:25:53,549 --> 00:25:55,390
I had no idea.

397
00:25:56,219 --> 00:25:58,890
I've blamed myself for everything
all my life.

398
00:25:59,890 --> 00:26:03,499
I've regretted everything
I've ever done.

399
00:26:05,430 --> 00:26:06,999
You could've...

400
00:26:07,299 --> 00:26:10,969
You could've told me
it wasn't my fault at least once.

401
00:26:11,200 --> 00:26:14,039
- Myeong Hee.
- If only you'd told me...

402
00:26:15,340 --> 00:26:18,039
If you'd only told me...

403
00:26:18,080 --> 00:26:20,610
why I must live in silence once.

404
00:26:22,309 --> 00:26:25,019
Then I wouldn't have gotten
my hopes up for nothing.

405
00:26:26,080 --> 00:26:28,190
Why did you have to make a fool
out of me?

406
00:26:28,420 --> 00:26:32,789
Why do I have to get shoved
into the ground without knowing why?

407
00:26:33,059 --> 00:26:34,590
Answer me!

408
00:26:34,759 --> 00:26:36,999
Answer me, Father!

409
00:26:47,840 --> 00:26:49,768
You little...

410
00:26:49,769 --> 00:26:53,478
You despicable little wench!

411
00:26:53,479 --> 00:26:57,978
Were you sent by Hwang Ki Nam too?

412
00:26:57,979 --> 00:27:01,018
- Go away!
- Mother, please calm down.

413
00:27:01,019 --> 00:27:03,589
- Let go!
- Hurry up and unplug the phone.

414
00:27:03,590 --> 00:27:05,659
Take Mother away.

415
00:27:05,660 --> 00:27:08,389
- Mother, calm down.
- How dare you show up here?

416
00:27:08,390 --> 00:27:11,058
- That's enough.
- Take me instead!

417
00:27:11,059 --> 00:27:12,958
- Mother!
- Get lost!

418
00:27:12,959 --> 00:27:14,100
Mother!

419
00:27:14,299 --> 00:27:18,399
My goodness. My son is innocent.
Why are you taking him?

420
00:27:18,400 --> 00:27:20,340
Sir, just a second, please.

421
00:27:21,739 --> 00:27:25,610
Mother, they're just going to ask me
a few questions.

422
00:27:25,779 --> 00:27:29,680
Like you said, I'm innocent.
You don't have to worry.

423
00:27:29,880 --> 00:27:32,779
Honey, see you later.

424
00:27:33,049 --> 00:27:34,589
See you.

425
00:27:34,590 --> 00:27:37,519
- Be careful.
- Hyun Chul.

426
00:27:38,559 --> 00:27:40,330
- My goodness.
- Wait.

427
00:28:04,420 --> 00:28:05,620
Ki Nam.

428
00:28:06,779 --> 00:28:08,748
You're Hwang Ki Nam, right?

429
00:28:08,749 --> 00:28:10,319
It's been a while, Hyun Chul.

430
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:15,130
Goodness. Ki Nam.

431
00:28:16,630 --> 00:28:18,430
My leg hurts so much.

432
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:20,569
I'm didn't do anything wrong.

433
00:28:21,499 --> 00:28:23,499
You know that.

434
00:28:24,140 --> 00:28:25,969
My father passed away.

435
00:28:26,700 --> 00:28:30,068
