because of your father.

458
00:30:13,610 --> 00:30:14,880
I should get going.

459
00:30:32,559 --> 00:30:33,700
Myeong Hee!

460
00:30:50,350 --> 00:30:53,019
I thought it would end
if I just stayed quiet.

461
00:30:56,650 --> 00:30:57,690
I didn't want you...

462
00:30:59,759 --> 00:31:02,190
to have to worry about such stigma.

463
00:31:04,029 --> 00:31:06,700
I wanted to break it off
so you wouldn't be affected.

464
00:31:16,440 --> 00:31:18,209
But it didn't stop with you.

465
00:31:36,789 --> 00:31:37,799
Myeong Hee...

466
00:31:59,179 --> 00:32:00,948
She still hasn't come home yet?

467
00:32:00,949 --> 00:32:03,419
She must be working overtime.

468
00:32:04,359 --> 00:32:06,619
I called the hospital,
and they said she wasn't there.

469
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:08,760
And I can't reach
her family in Naju.

470
00:32:09,090 --> 00:32:12,358
She must be on a trip or something.
Myeong Hee isn't a kid.

471
00:32:12,359 --> 00:32:14,529
Why is everyone making a fuss
looking for her?

472
00:32:14,530 --> 00:32:17,439
Goodness gracious. Go on home, okay?

473
00:32:20,199 --> 00:32:22,310
If you give me a chance,

474
00:32:22,570 --> 00:32:26,280
