476
00:32:33,379 --> 00:32:34,689
Several months?

477
00:32:38,260 --> 00:32:40,989
I see. Then please call me
as soon as you find out...

478
00:32:40,990 --> 00:32:43,659
about the part
I asked about earlier.

479
00:32:45,330 --> 00:32:47,668
Soo Chan. What's going on here?

480
00:32:47,669 --> 00:32:49,829
Soo Ryeon.
I'm a little busy right now.

481
00:32:49,830 --> 00:32:50,869
Let's talk at home.

482
00:32:52,939 --> 00:32:54,270
What's this?

483
00:32:56,010 --> 00:32:58,580
Passport... Visa...

484
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:01,679
